{"tid":883713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多圖【胸大的煩惱】靚女名記自曝做縮胸手術","createTime":"2018-10-31T04:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T08:56:36.000Z","uid":147522,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"936088befa423facaea6b23813c82ed0c552cb26","tid":883713,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:50:24.000Z","msg":"　　<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/31/125014_1a5021dd5f682565794d501f52328e03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F125014_1a5021dd5f682565794d501f52328e03.png&h=e3819cfc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/31/125018_2c52534ee791705215e62a866934667d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F125018_2c52534ee791705215e62a866934667d.png&h=8f830176&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/31/125021_e3bf9f15a3e6a90ed72d4f652d521ed8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2F125021_e3bf9f15a3e6a90ed72d4f652d521ed8.png&h=96f46010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n        據《鏡報》報導，ESPN美女記者娜蒂-若塔已決定做縮胸手術，因為她希望人們能夠嚴肅對待自己。<br />\n<br />\n　　24歲的娜蒂是阿根廷人，她表示自己在說話的時候，人們總是不看自己的臉，她說道：「在學校的時候，我的同學都開始發育，我還沒有，我就經常被人叫飛機場、平胸妹之類的。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「當我的閨蜜都在祈禱白馬王子出現的時候，我祈禱自己能長胸，所以老話說得對，要慎重許願，我得到了胸，而現在我要做手術去將它們變小。」<br />\n<br />\n　　娜蒂還稱做縮胸手術也是為了健康著想，因為她現在常常因胸部太大而背痛，而且很難找到合身的衣服<br />\n<br />\n　　這位金髮女郎在Twitter上有85萬粉絲，其Instagram的關注者更是超過百萬，最近她在家人和男友的陪同下錄製了一段視頻，向粉絲們表示自己的縮胸手術很成功。"},{"pid":"32f35f73c62fd7b87c05b55a988ec5914e3bbac1","tid":883713,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:51:28.000Z","msg":"呢d就有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2ab611a42c2dcd91846266ffbc7769d7eaf0b9","tid":883713,"uid":58335,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:53:43.000Z","msg":"暴殄天物"},{"pid":"a388db29410843b67fa72a0dfc270a1209691601","tid":883713,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6921fdf20ed59a143c3ed6117457e3b024900671","tid":883713,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"以為梁凱寧冇做香港早晨去做手術"},{"pid":"414922e43cf79e66e67d89b915d02772be4b8db8","tid":883713,"uid":59929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:02:30.000Z","msg":"減肥個胸咪細"},{"pid":"8546844ba87ea87e865c5ad18bcdf01b4ecc555b","tid":883713,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:24:05.000Z","msg":"唔睇外國新聞，都唔知道原來有呢種手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff562a882a2a3017a0e06dbfbce8bbbe82db96f","tid":883713,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:25:06.000Z","msg":"下世做平胸女人唔好喊"},{"pid":"ed5dfe3d57068931ec64240ff17ab8cdb026cc5d","tid":883713,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"我可以伸出援手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea17d48320c47062b7e703ea2b59cb0cff884ce","tid":883713,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T07:59:31.000Z","msg":"對波重到墮,唔慌靚"},{"pid":"6a55af9acec220a4d6092030482abf6398c4f5bc","tid":883713,"uid":118463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8546844ba87ea87e865c5ad18bcdf01b4ecc555b","tid":883713,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T05:24:05.000Z","msg":"唔睇外國新聞，都唔知道原來有呢種手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T08:02:34.000Z","msg":"香港冇需要做"},{"pid":"f1b959b722285b7a4813d505da4af2e0ca5a09cf","tid":883713,"uid":35045,"like":2,"dislike":